Added standard CRUD UI views (list, detail, add/edit, delete, bulk edit/delete) for the IPAddressRange model.
Added an "IP Address Ranges" tab to the Prefix detail view listing the ranges contained within a Prefix.
Added an IP Address Ranges panel to the Role detail view for roles associated with the IPAddressRange content type.
Added REST API for the IPAddressRange model.
Added IPAddressRange filtering by name, namespace, parent Prefix, start/end address, and by an address contained within a range.
